title: Žan Zaletel
text:
Žan Zaletel (born 16 September 1999) is a Slovenian <a href="association%20football">football</a>er who plays for <a href="NK%20Celje">Celje</a> as a <a href="Defender%20%28association%20football%29">defender</a>.
Club career.
Zaletel made his <a href="Slovenian%20PrvaLiga">Slovenian PrvaLiga</a> debut for <a href="NK%20Celje">Celje</a> on 20 July 2018 in a game against <a href="NK%20Aluminij">Aluminij</a>.
